<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Shipping Policy</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles.css"> <!-- Add your custom styles -->
</head>
<body>
    <%- include('partials/header') %>

    <div class="container mt-5">
        <h1>Shipping Policy</h1>
        <p>Our shipping policy outlines the terms and conditions for delivering orders to you.</p>

        <h2>1. Shipping Areas</h2>
        <p>We deliver to specified areas within Rahata/A.nagar. Please check our delivery areas before placing an order.</p>

        <h2>2. Delivery Time</h2>
        <p>Delivery times vary based on your location and traffic conditions. We aim to deliver within 1/2 or Max 1 hours of order confirmation.</p>

        <h2>3. Delivery Charges</h2>
        <p>Delivery charges are calculated based on the distance from our restaurant. Charges are displayed during the checkout process.</p>

        <h2>4. Order Tracking</h2>
        <p>Once your order is dispatched, you will receive a tracking number to monitor its status.</p>

        <h2>5. Contact Us</h2>
        <p>If you have any questions about shipping, please contact us.</p>
    </div>

    <%- include('partials/footer') %>
</body>
</html>
